<block a:if="{{showCalendar}}"><view class="calendar-content"><text class="example-info">日历组件可以查看日期，选择任意范围内的日期，打点操作。常用场景如：酒店日期预订、火车机票选择购买日期、上下班打卡等。</text><uni-section vue-id="4f64af70-1" title="插入模式" type="line" onVueInit="__l"></uni-section><view><uni-calendar class="uni-calendar--hook" vue-id="4f64af70-2" selected="{{info.selected}}" showMonth="{{false}}" data-event-opts="{{[['^change',[['change']]],['^monthSwitch',[['monthSwitch']]]]}}" onChange="__e" onMonthSwitch="__e" onVueInit="__l"></uni-calendar></view><uni-section vue-id="4f64af70-3" title="弹出模式" type="line" onVueInit="__l"></uni-section><view class="example-body"><button class="calendar-button" type="button" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['open',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">打开日历</button></view><uni-calendar class="uni-calendar--hook" vue-id="4f64af70-4" clear-date="{{true}}" date="{{info.date}}" insert="{{info.insert}}" lunar="{{info.lunar}}" startDate="{{info.startDate}}" endDate="{{info.endDate}}" range="{{info.range}}" ref="__r" data-ref="calendar" data-event-opts="{{[['^confirm',[['confirm']]],['^close',[['close']]]]}}" onConfirm="__e" onClose="__e" onVueInit="__l"></uni-calendar></view></block>